name: Expression SketchFlow Feedback File
summary: Learn about .FEEDBACK files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: FEEDBACK files can be imported into an Expression SketchFlow project so application designers can review the feedback.

description: File created by Microsoft Expression SketchFlow, a program used for designing media and Web applications; contains feedback for a design that is stored in a .FLOW file; may include redline markups and comments; used by reviewers for submitting feedback to the design team.
